    "body": "Those mock-ups look purdy. Does the tabbed design mean that people would be able to connect to multiple servers at once? If so, that might be exploited by people with malicious intent to hog player slots or even whole servers.\n\nAnother thing that would be nice is to show more information on the map in the lobby (whether it has custom rules, the description text and so on).\n\nAlso, just as food for thought: maybe the players and options bin could be implemented as tabs as well. (And the (extended) map info could then be a third tab, maybe.). I always found it odd to change the panels with a button. That might waste too much vertical space, though.\n"
  },
