    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Some changes after some feedback from @pchote and @obrakmann; @pchote plans to implement these screens soon.\n\nBoth screens\n- The chat bin, server bin, and lobby bin, and even side panel bin are all a uniform size, so switching between the two screens looks seamless.\n\nServer Browser\n- Added a lock icon if the server is passworded\n- Also show map spawns and who has taken them.\n\nLobby\n- Added map description in a scroll-able panel.\n- Added a warning icon (tool tip to indicate as well) if the map has custom `Rules:` defined\n- Moved some buttons around, and made the lobby buttons into tabs\n\n![browser](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/566742/10266213/5bda1e76-6a11-11e5-8cc3-d535fe8d3249.png)\n![lobby](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/566742/10266215/5f2f88f4-6a11-11e5-89da-509949b0f389.png)\n"
  },
