    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Works well for the TD special case UI, but it is a bit confusing and prone to mis-clicks for the rest of the mods with chat and game disconnect right next to each other.\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/756669/10628220/064a11d6-77c3-11e5-8c31-0682854e0388.png)\n\nI suggest you add the start game button near the lobby stuff. There is still some space to save when giving the buttons appropriate widths and removing the mostly empty bottom line:\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/756669/10628227/230bda20-77c3-11e5-822d-a107f4eca0d5.png)\n\n`Leave game` and `Change map` placement isn't optimal then, but I don't have a better idea yet.\n"
  },
