    "body": "Initial rough design of the server browser:\n\n![browser](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/167819/10679344/e4f5ba28-790f-11e5-9801-014e81f8a097.png)\n\nThe check / cross were placeholders for status icons for password protected servers and state.  Based on feedback i'm going to go back to a short colored status label (playing/waiting/empty) and will move the password icon to the front of the player column.  The info below the map preview will also change.\n"
